<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #ef4444 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .security-alert {
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #b91c1c;
    }
    .link-box {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a5568;
    }
    .steps {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .step-number {
      background: #f0f4ff;
      color: #4f46e5;
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-right: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        padding: 30px 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
      <p style="opacity: 0.9; margin-top: 10px;">Secure your Assessly account</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        Hello,<br>
        We received a request to reset your password for your Assessly account. Click the button below to create a new password.
      </p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta-button">Reset Password</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="link-box">
        <strong>Or copy this link:</strong><br>
        {{resetUrl}}
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-alert">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #b91c1c;">
          <strong>🔒 Security Notice:</strong><br>
          This password reset link will expire in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>. 
          If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you're concerned about your account's security.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="steps">
        <p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 15px;">Follow these steps to secure your account:</p>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Click the reset button above</strong><br>
            <span style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px;">You'll be taken to a secure page to create your new password</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Create a strong password</strong><br>
            <span style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px;">Use at least 12 characters with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Sign in with your new password</strong><br>
            <span style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 14px;">You'll be automatically logged in after resetting your password</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
          <strong>Need help?</strong><br>
          If you're having trouble resetting your password or have questions about your account security, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@assessly.com" style="color: #4f46e5;">support@assessly.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Assessly Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.7;">
        This is an automated security email from Assessly. Please do not reply to this message.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
